M||tx|---
M||name|mk-ps
M||desc|>-
M||tx|"When the us wants to apply psychological principles, mental md, or behavioral science to mk. Also use when the us mentions 'ps,' 'mental md,' 'cognitive bias,' 'persuasion,' 'behavioral science,' 'why people buy,' 'decision-making,' 'consumer behavior,' 'anchoring,' 'sl proof,' 'scarcity,' 'loss aversion,' 'framing,' or 'nudge.' Use this whenever someone wants to understand or leverage how people think and make decisions in a mk context."
