M|Quic|tx|\| Increasing urgency \| Scarcity, Loss Aversion, Zeigarnik Effect \|
M|Quic|tx|\| Retention/churn \| Endowment Effect, Switching Costs, Status-Quo Bias \|
M|Quic|tx|\| Growth stalling \| Theory of Constraints, Local vs Global Optima, Compounding \|
M|Quic|tx|\| Decision paralysis \| Paradox of Choice, Default Effect, Nudge Theory \|
M|Quic|tx|\| Onboarding \| Goal-Gradient, IKEA Effect, Commitment & Consistency \|
M|Quic|tx|---
M|Task|tx|1. What specific behavior are you trying to influence?
M|Task|tx|2. What does your cs believe before encountering your mk?
M|Task|tx|3. Where in the journey (awareness → consideration → decision) is this?
M|Task|tx|4. What's currently preventing the desired action?
M|Task|tx|5. Have you tested this w/ real cs?
M|Task|tx|---
